thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by Kevin

author: Kevin
title: Kevin
text: Ordered frames, mats, mounting boards, acrylic plates and several accessories. Packaging was excellent and all items were of great quality and cut exactly to my specifications. One of the acrylic plates had a scratch, which could not have been noticed by the frame shop (or me) until the paper was removed; this item was replaced promptly and the customer service rep couldn't have been nicer. Overall a very positive experience and I would(and have) buy from them again. Highly recommended.
